{"tid":580300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李嘉誠入股Facebook","createTime":"2018-03-04T11:48:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T12:28:58.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"965e9be6fc972608e2a019c6330a0be3bce6b887","tid":580300,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:48:41.000Z","msg":"據網站《<a href=\"http://AllThingsD.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAllThingsD.com&d=fOLDslNAwYliePqxex7p70kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=2aa8b588\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AllThingsD.com</a>》引述消息人士透露，長實（001）主席李嘉誠以私人名義，斥資6000萬美元（約4.68億元）入股社交網站Facebook。正如早年的MySpace及YouTube網站一樣，加入Facebook社交網站的熱潮正席捲全球，更引來不少名人參加。報道上述消息的網站，正是美國《華爾街日報》改革網上新聞後，專為科技及媒體而設的網誌。<br />\n<br />\n涉資4.68億<br />\n<br />\n和黃（013）發言人對消息不予置評。報道指，李嘉誠投資Facebook，是因為一名Facebook投資者將這家公司介紹給其好友周凱旋，後者除了是李嘉誠基金會的董事外，亦是TOM集團（2383）的主要股東之一，而李嘉誠則透過旗下長和系持有TOM集團部分權益。消息人士稱，是次入股後，可能會幫助TOM成為Facebook的中國合作夥伴。<br />\n根據協定，李嘉誠有權再向Facebook增資6000萬美元。不過，亦不是所有企業甘冒風險，報道指出，有風險投資公司因Facebook要求的條款過於苛刻而放棄；如ProvidenceEquity便因條款中缺乏對投資者的保護，亦不能加入Facebook董事局，最終放棄入股。至於微軟和李嘉誠亦一樣，入股亦不能獲得董事會席位。<br />\nFacebook是一個社交網站，創辦於04年，今年10月獲微軟斥資2.4億美元收購1.6%的權益。以此計算，其沽值達150億美元（1170億元）。當時公司透露，全球活躍用戶逾5000萬，並以每日新增20萬用戶的速度增長。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20071201/large/01bc8pa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20071201%2Flarge%2F01bc8pa.jpg&h=a22af079&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李嘉誠以私人名義入股社交網站Facebook。　資料圖片<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20071201/10482202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20071201%2F10482202&d=fOLDslNAwYliePqxex7p70kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=53cd01a8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20071201%2F10482202&h=6470009d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20071201/10482202</a>"},{"pid":"c41bf17ab159088a83bba20866ea5cdca627b307","tid":580300,"uid":5190,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:49:31.000Z","msg":"Facebook for 老餅用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f6ff6c6c21856e13c421fee6fde899dbeb7bef","tid":580300,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/17/142556_b14f0a4a6cd1ebbac3e71dfcf1ab98b2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F17%2F142556_b14f0a4a6cd1ebbac3e71dfcf1ab98b2.png&h=57b4121a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3c431a26fe4361f28d6935e118bc5bef3c61b17f","tid":580300,"uid":1646,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"20071201"},{"pid":"5eb06be5da19d33a92a3bdd9a9e1d34c3bd5544e","tid":580300,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"開始冇人用先入股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n★FaceBook玩完！朱克伯格頻頻沽售Fb股票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/571439/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/571439/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"353d77121b7e1eb34c46fa1178c9e4ee3c555bdf","tid":580300,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5eb06be5da19d33a92a3bdd9a9e1d34c3bd5544e","tid":580300,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T11:52:01.000Z","msg":"開始冇人用先入股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n★FaceBook玩完！朱克伯格頻頻沽售Fb股票<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/571439/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/threa